# code.md — Reference Website Micro Store (Astro + Tailwind CSS)

## Tujuan Document

Document ini digunakan sebagai acuan development website dengan style minimalis modern menggunakan:

* Astro
* Tailwind CSS
* Component-based architecture
* Responsive layout
* Clean storefront UI

Document ini dibuat agar programmer junior dapat memahami:

* Struktur layout
* Styling system
* Component yang digunakan
* Rules UI/UX
* Struktur folder
* Best practice development

---

# 1. Konsep Website

## Style Website

Website menggunakan konsep:

* Minimalis modern
* Clean whitespace
* Fokus pada produk visual
* Typography besar dan ringan
* Soft rounded card
* Dominasi warna netral
* Accent color orange
* Grid layout simetris

Inspirasi visual:

* Apple style
* Modern startup landing page
* Product showcase website
* Minimal ecommerce storefront

---

# 2. Stack Technology

## Core Stack

```txt
Framework : Astro
Styling    : Tailwind CSS
Deploy     : Vercel / Netlify
Image      : Astro Image / WebP
Font       : Inter / Geist / Plus Jakarta Sans
```

---

# 3. Design Rules

## Background

Gunakan warna:

```css
background: #f3f3f3;
```

Atau:

```css
bg-neutral-100
```

---

## Typography

### Heading

Karakteristik:

* Bold
* Besar
* Clean
* Tight spacing
* Center aligned

Contoh:

```txt
A sleek Astro & Tailwind CSS template for modern storefronts.
```

Tailwind:

```html
text-5xl
font-semibold
tracking-tight
leading-tight
```

---

### Description Text

Karakteristik:

* Abu terang
* Tipis
* Secondary information

Tailwind:

```html
text-neutral-500
text-sm
```

---

## Accent Color

Gunakan warna orange:

```css
#ff6b3d
```

Digunakan untuk:

* Button primary
* Harga produk
* Hover state
* CTA

