# 7. Product Card

## Struktur Card

```txt
Image
Title + Price
Description
```

---

## Card Style

Karakteristik:

* Rounded besar
* Overflow hidden
* Clean
* Hover smooth
* Tidak banyak shadow

Tailwind:

```html
rounded-3xl
overflow-hidden
transition
hover:-translate-y-1
```

---

## Product Image

Karakteristik:

* Fokus visual utama
* Rasio landscape
* Cover image
* Rounded image

Tailwind:

```html
aspect-[4/3]
object-cover
w-full
```

Gunakan:

* WebP
* Compress image
* Lazy loading

---

