# 9. Spacing Rules

## Gunakan spacing besar

Contoh:

```txt
Section padding besar
Card gap besar
Whitespace dominan
```

Tailwind:

```html
py-24
gap-10
space-y-6
```

Tujuan:

* Website terlihat premium
* Tidak sesak
* Fokus visual lebih jelas

---

# 10. Responsive Rules

## Mobile First

Selalu gunakan:

```txt
Mobile → Tablet → Desktop
```

Contoh:

```html
text-3xl md:text-5xl
px-4 md:px-8
```

---

# 11. Animation Rules

## Gunakan animation ringan

Hanya gunakan:

* Hover lift
* Fade
* Scale kecil
* Smooth transition

Jangan gunakan:

* Animation berlebihan
* Slider berat
* Auto popup
* Parallax berat

Tailwind:

```html
transition-all
duration-300
ease-out
```

---

# 12. Performance Rules

## Wajib Optimasi

### Image

Gunakan:

* WebP
* Lazy loading
* Compressed image
* Responsive image

---

### Hindari

```txt
Slider berat
Video autoplay besar
JS tidak perlu
Library terlalu banyak
```

---

## Target Performance

```txt
Lighthouse > 90
CLS rendah
LCP cepat
SEO optimal
```

---

